From db91a847a2b6d383e29b331f7319db2bcde6612e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: j <jvdelorenzi@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 14 Apr 2026 22:04:15 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 1/2] fix: replace hardcoded hex colors with CSS design tokens
 across 17 files

Systematic design system consolidation: migrated ~1300 hardcoded hex color
values to CSS custom properties from tokens.css. Removed duplicate
tailwind.config.js module.exports (155 lines of dead code). Added missing
focus-visible state on .mcv-input for accessibility.

Files: tailwind.config.js, components.css, Footer, ServerHero, ServerContent,
layout, globals, homepage, pricing, cases, judges, search, calculator,
dashboard, odds, report, fee-calculator pages.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
